{"tid":1929022,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"歐盟：旅客禁入境神根地區30日","createTime":"2020-03-16T17:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T17:40:58.000Z","uid":320405,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f4bb23f5e1b70d62737040adab811c5b9b6b3e7e","tid":1929022,"uid":320405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒疫情在歐洲急速惡化，歐盟委員會主席馮德萊恩表示，為防範新冠病毒疫情擴散，將實施臨時30日入境禁令，禁制非必要的外國旅客入境神根地區。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐洲神根地區包括奧地利、比利時、捷克、丹麥、愛沙尼亞、芬蘭、法國、德國、希臘、匈牙利、冰島、意大利、拉脫維亞、列支敦士登、立陶宛、盧森堡、馬耳他、荷蘭、挪威、波蘭、葡萄牙、斯洛伐克、斯洛文尼亞、西班牙、瑞典及瑞士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200316/s00005/1584373732350\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200316%2Fs00005%2F1584373732350&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8JUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=4c42031f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%2Farticle%2F20200316%2Fs00005%2F1584373732350&h=efba1eaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b/article/20200316/s00005/1584373732350</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國脫歐重大成果：<br />\n唔被歐盟封關，可以繼續佛系治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a71413f6f20883c9791a90a32112ac2fcab12bb4","tid":1929022,"uid":38795,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T17:08:21.000Z","msg":"英國一直都唔係神根區"},{"pid":"4764591014713c159bf9c32cd104c477ce90d38e","tid":1929022,"uid":20170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T17:09:55.000Z","msg":"英國喺歐盟時期，一樣唔係神根一份子"},{"pid":"8d664a93804a8fcbbcd51a374c3dd8f0913c503a","tid":1929022,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T17:10:42.000Z","msg":"終於識封關<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/h